{"tid":2085548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南海升溫 解放軍封西沙演練  美兩航母晒馬 震懾中國","createTime":"2020-06-30T02:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T04:21:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4a7ee31fa10a7fae05e721aaeed38468007518","tid":2085548,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200630/CRGTIJJ33D6EGZ5V227JPXCQJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200630%2FCRGTIJJ33D6EGZ5V227JPXCQJU%2F&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CDkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=d8ba9bd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200630%2FCRGTIJJ33D6EGZ5V227JPXCQJU%2F&h=1c69d8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200630/CRGTIJJ33D6EGZ5V227JPXCQJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n南海升溫 解放軍封西沙演練 <br />\n美兩航母晒馬 震懾中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美中兩國又在南海「晒馬」。美國海軍28日宣佈，包括尼米茲號（CVN-68）和列根號（CVN-76）兩大航空母艦戰鬥群，開始在菲律賓海舉行聯合軍事演習，以展示美軍已準備好應對所有挑戰國際準則的勢力，劍指北京。中國軍方亦在同日宣佈，明日起一連五日在南海西沙群島周邊海域舉行軍演。有軍事專家指，美中緊張關係不斷升級之際，兩國海軍在相鄰海域幾乎同步舉行軍演，針鋒相對，一旦失控發生危機，兩國將陷災難。<br />\n<br />\n外媒引述美國海軍表示，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n即海軍南海艦隊參演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FOt1NEicZEZUz1eOK__Rb-U2jBo=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CCJR7FEYWIUKYDG7M6ONWIMNI4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFOt1NEicZEZUz1eOK__Rb-U2jBo%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCCJR7FEYWIUKYDG7M6ONWIMNI4.gif&h=15746d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國海軍前日開始再有兩支航母戰鬥群在菲律賓海軍演；圖為羅斯福號（前左）和尼米茲號（前右）上周演練情況。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m9HUMPw1q7U7G5Op5MB564zYREM=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XWZYRNFT2HZX6MYAQFSGXIERJQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm9HUMPw1q7U7G5Op5MB564zYREM%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXWZYRNFT2HZX6MYAQFSGXIERJQ.gif&h=54b10548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國山東艦現駐紮三亞基地，但尚在組裝未能出戰。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BpZooYJNiowBpTJYtE6fGnM3fL0=/190x117/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5PN7OHEDJ4O3YQPPTVSCNYGIQI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBpZooYJNiowBpTJYtE6fGnM3fL0%3D%2F190x117%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5PN7OHEDJ4O3YQPPTVSCNYGIQI.gif&h=d8fce50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍戰機從航母上起飛。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T7N_houtB-eEhFjd8_BeSavb9VQ=/190x166/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IHOFU6UPMHQCETXCI6NYQW2AWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT7N_houtB-eEhFjd8_BeSavb9VQ%3D%2F190x166%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIHOFU6UPMHQCETXCI6NYQW2AWY.gif&h=dacb3087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正參與演習的美軍人員檢查艦載戰機。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘擦槍走火將陷災難<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美軍公開赴台聯合訓練片段<br />\n<br />\n按美軍配置，一個航母戰鬥群通常<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n而尼米茲號及羅斯福號戰鬥群更於6月21日已在菲律賓海進行過聯合演習。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，南海艦隊是中共海軍三大艦隊中防禦海域最大、實力最強的艦隊，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，並擁有兩個海軍陸戰旅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q-g8cPNFKgKjoqr4ET2ASGMgNoM=/190x121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YGWELWHKT2VFEUAMSU7DQ22QXA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ-g8cPNFKgKjoqr4ET2ASGMgNoM%3D%2F190x121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYGWELWHKT2VFEUAMSU7DQ22QXA.gif&h=c584b624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍機飛往南海疑偵測<br />\n<br />\n近年美國拒絕承認中方在南海填海造島，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n中方每次都派艦船跟蹤、警告和驅離美艦。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美軍多架P-8A偵察機、C-40A運輸機、KC-135R加油機、RC-135U及EP-3E電子偵察機等，昨紛現蹤巴士海峽，飛往南海，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n中共近期頻向鄰國「騷肌肉」，旨在對抗華盛頓。"},{"pid":"be258aeb46ff215ec91fe42bb1b436841daada70","tid":2085548,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"騷肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全副武裝連咖哩都打唔嬴講呢D"},{"pid":"fdd58eae14b4f6ee62270bae23f3029306273c17","tid":2085548,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be258aeb46ff215ec91fe42bb1b436841daada70","tid":2085548,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"騷肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全副武裝連咖哩都打唔嬴講呢D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec60f373f9c930428b129181395128ede66885d0","tid":2085548,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"好悶呀"},{"pid":"fecbc30ba50ef80524ad21b9a35b28d697217a44","tid":2085548,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be258aeb46ff215ec91fe42bb1b436841daada70","tid":2085548,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"騷肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全副武裝連咖哩都打唔嬴講呢D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"仲要係冇作戰經驗既海軍。"},{"pid":"1fa7cae7b8093267c8afb379f1b40fe10a6418a9","tid":2085548,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"乜依家仲興晒馬？<br />\n直接無人機斬首啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}